# Allowlist: dist/ (Netlify publish target) plus the source build tooling. content/ stays local, never committed.

*

!.gitignore
!netlify.toml
!README.md
!docs/
!docs/**
!dist/
!dist/**

# Source build tooling (versioned for recovery; no secrets in these)
!build_static_site.py
!config.yml
!watch_and_build.ps1
!run_build_scheduled.bat
!serve.py

# Build output copies of trash / local junk — never ship
**/desktop.ini
dist/.trash/
dist/assets/md_hashes.json
dist/site.pdf
